snippet.title: For ANYONE Who Still Believes AH Was the Victim
snippet.description: This is a short painful video that shows actual pictures of just some of the physical abuse Johnny Depp suffered at the claws of amber heard.  if you can look at these images and still call her the victim then you are just simply blind and well,  dumb.  I honestly don't care if you are offended by my words,  you are welcome to go elsewhere if you think that she is innocent.
